      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should expect the typical cosmetic and mechanical wear associated with a well-used vehicle. It is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
