      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi Q7 Premium Plus that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior, finished in a deep Moonlight Blue Metallic, retains a high-gloss luster; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood from normal highway use, the body is remarkably straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin featuring Nougat Brown leather seats that remain supple and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All technological features, including the Virtual Cockpit, panoramic sunroof, and the Bose 3D Surround Sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this SUV is in excellent health with a documented service history. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes are sharp and the tires have significant tread remaining. This is a reliable, high-end family vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
